<span style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal;\">n</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.4em;\">&nbsp;нь маш том тоо байж болохыг анхаарна уу (ѳѳрѳѳр хэлбэл таны ашиглаж байгаа програмчлалын хэлний бүхэл тоон утгын заагаас хэтэрсэн байж болно).</span></span></p>\n<h3>Input</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.6000003814697px;\">Ганц мѳрѳнд&nbsp;<span style=\"white-space: nowrap; color: #000000;\">n</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.6000003814697px;\">&nbsp;(</span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-5-Frame\" style=\"display: inline; word-wrap: normal; white-space: nowrap; float: none; direction: ltr; max-width: none; max-height: none; min-width: 0px; min-height: 0px; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-47\" style=\"-webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline-block; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; width: 7.443em;\"><span style=\"display: inline-block; position: relative; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; width: 6.193em; height: 0px;\"><span id=\"MathJax-Span-49\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\">0</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-50\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"> </span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-51\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.182em; margin: 0px;\">≤</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-52\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"> </span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-53\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.182em; margin: 0px;\">n</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-54\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0